author: Mark Molloy
title: Angela Merkel's candlelit dinner with Justin Trudeau sparks memes
text:
News Angela Merkel's candlelit dinner with Justin Trudeau sparks memes Angela Merkel and Canada's Prime Minister Justin Trudeau during a private meeting at the Regent hotel in Berlin Credit: Reuters Mark Molloy 17 February 2017 • 1:10pm 
A ngel Merkel became the latest world leader to meet with Canadian prime minister Justin Trudeau and surprised him with a gift before the pair sat down for a candlelit dinner - sparking a host of memes on Twitter. 
The German chancellor presented Trudeau with a photo of taken when he was ten, accompanying his father Pierre Trudeau to a meeting with German Chancellor Helmut Kohl on 12 November 1982. Merkel and Trudeau meet Credit: Reuters 
P hotos of Trudeau and Merkel’s dinner at the Regent hotel in Berlin have been shared on social media, sparking jokes about the pair appearing to be enjoying a ‘date night’. German chancellor Angela Merkel welcomes Canada's prime minister Justin Trudeau Credit: Reuters There were plenty of memes and jokes I'm glad Angela Merkel and Justin Trudeau had a nice date pic.twitter.com/2uyRM9PRDJ — Elena Cresci (@elenacresci) February 17, 2017 @elenacresci PM "Steal yo Girl" at it again.... — Adi Peltz (@adi_peltz) February 17, 2017 @elenacresci @MartinBelam Ivanka must be fuming. Expect an imminent ban on all German imports — Henrik Asbjørnsen (@henrik2a) February 17, 2017 Now even Merkel. One more for the genre "married women meeting Justin" (cc @blairelliott ). #Trudeau pic.twitter.com/vJjmmqRayt — Maximilian Miguletz (@max_migu) February 17, 2017 Was ein Bild! Kann grad in die Reihe mit Ivanka und Kate. #Trudeau #loveisintheair https://t.co/AsLGo7lKst — Maximilian Miguletz (@max_migu) February 17, 2017 Never thought I'd be jealous of Angela Merkel but here we go... candlelight dinner with Justin Trudeau.
